title: AHS: DOUBLE FEATURE Episode 4 Preview Breakdown & Theories! - "Blood Buffet"
author: Think Story
comment:
What do you think will happen in episode 4? 




Check out my episode 3 breakdown video here: https://youtu.be/ZJV1SXNQJ2A
Can wait for the flash back episode and to see what the black pills are made of
Evan Peters is not giving me a Frank from Rocky horror vibe but rather a Hedwig and the angry inch vibe which would make more sense for him becoming a writer of contemporary musicals
Oh shit maybe we'll get to see how the other characters first took the Black Pill or how someone turns into a pale creature.
This has been a great season so far.  Very much appreciated!
